Uses of Package
model

  • Packages that use model 
    Package Description
    client.GUI
    Contains all the JavaFX GUI implementations
    client.clientController
    Contains the classes that the server invokes or calls to push information to the client
    client.remoteController
    Contains the classes used to send messages to the server
    commons
    Contains all different classes that are common between server and client
    controller
    Contains all the different controllers, the main logic of the game is here
    model
    Describes all the Adrenaline game objects and parts
    model.ammo
    Contains a lot of ammo
    model.map
    Contains all the classes used to describe the arenas
    model.player
    Contains all the classes used to model a player
    model.powerup
    Contains all the powerUp cards definitions, effects and deck
    model.weapons
    This class contains all the weapons definitions, effects, deck
    server.RMIHandler
    Contains all the classes to manage the RMI connections
